# is-not-null-of-null

## Description

Migrated from the hand-coded `null_simplification_rules` to a declarative `.rra` rule
(RFC 0090). The rewrite is expressed as structured data below.

## Rewrite

lhs: (is-not-null const-null)
rhs: (const-bool false)
